OL,3,CWork starts to protect rare 'carbon
OL,4,Ccapture' seaweed discovered off the UK
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FOne of the largest amounts of a rare
OL,8,Ftype of seaweed ever discovered in the
OL,9,FUK has been uncovered off the coast of
OL,10,FCornwall.
OL,12,FThe vast seabed of maerl, a rare and
OL,13,Fancient seaweed, is equivalent to the
OL,14,Fsize of nearly 900 rugby pitches and
OL,15,Fis thought to be around 4,000 years
OL,16,Fold. It carpets the seafloor and
OL,17,Fprovides protection for many small
OL,18,Fmarine plants and animals.
