OL,3,CWork starts to protect rare 'carbon
OL,4,Ccapture' seaweed discovered off the UK
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FScientists discovered the seaweed in
OL,8,Fthe Fal and Helford Estuary Special
OL,9,FArea of Conservation
OL,11,FIt is extremely efficient at storing
OL,12,Fcarbon at an estimated rate of 841
OL,13,Ftonnes of CO2 every year, the
OL,14,Fequivalent to nearly 4,000,000 petrol
OL,15,Fcar miles a year and five times
OL,16,Fgreater than that absorbed by the
OL,17,Fcombined area of seagrass, kelp and
OL,18,Fsaltmarsh also in the same area.
