OL,3,CWork starts to protect rare 'carbon
OL,4,Ccapture' seaweed discovered off the UK
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FIt is the first time the full extent
OL,8,Fof the maerl beds and the organic
OL,9,Fmatter stored in the conservation area
OL,10,Fhas been measured with the discovery
OL,11,Fnow marking the location as a key
OL,12,Fnational site.
OL,14,FDr Chris Laing, Senior Lecturer in
OL,15,FMarine Biology at the University of
OL,16,FExeter and research lead on the
OL,17,Fproject said: "Maerl has not been
OL,18,Fconsidered as a valuable carbon store
OL,19,Fto date.
