OL,3,CWork starts to protect rare 'carbon
OL,4,Ccapture' seaweed discovered off the UK
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,F"Our research demonstrates that as
OL,8,Fwell as being a rare and valuable
OL,9,Fseabed habitat it should be a key
OL,10,Fplayer in coastal blue carbon
OL,11,Fassessments which is an extremely
OL,12,Fimportant discovery for Cornwall where
OL,13,Fthe extent of the maerl beds are
OL,14,Fsignificant."
