OL,3,CWork starts to protect rare 'carbon
OL,4,Ccapture' seaweed discovered off the UK
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FCornwall's cabinet member for
OL,8,Fenvironment and climate change Cllr
OL,9,FMartyn Alvey said: "The project shows
OL,10,Fhow these blue carbon habitats can
OL,11,Fhelp us in our response to both the
OL,12,Fclimate and ecological emergencies if
OL,13,Fwe properly protect them and allow
OL,14,Fthem to fully recover.
OL,16,F"We are working with partners to
OL,17,Fensure that these vital blue carbon
OL,18,Fecosystems are protected from threats
OL,19,Fsuch as poor water quality,
OL,20,Frecreational boating and nutrient
OL,21,Floading."
